projects.description:
Support to active and effective participation by States Parties in the Implementation Review Mechanism of UNCAC;
Supporting the capacity of anti-corruption practitioners and other stakeholders to prevent and combat corruption and implement the Regional Anti-Corruption and Illicit Finance Roadmap;
Support in mainstreaming anti-corruption into national development strategies and enhancing technical assistance programmes

The project will specifically focus on:
• enhancing the commitment and capacities of media and journalists to abide by professional and ethical standards of journalism and enhancing media accountability; 
• reinforcing freedom of expression and circulation of accurate information by an increasing rights-based regulation of digital platforms and online media;
